Package: numberFormattR
Type: Package
Title: This package lets you format numbers with suffixes, such as k, M, B for thousands, millions, and billions.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Matthias Raess, Ph.D.
Maintainer: Matthias Raess, Ph.D. <matthias.raess@gmail.com>
Description: This package lets you format numbers with suffixes, such as k, M, B for thousands, millions, and billions. It also has functions to format axes in ggplots with lettered numbers.
Depends: tidyverse
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1.9000
